# PantheonOS Trademark Policy v1.0

“PantheonOS”, “Pantheon-Prime”, and the PantheonOS logo are trademarks of B.H.

These marks MAY be used for:
- Accurate reference to the open-source project
- Tutorials, documentation, educational resources
- Community forks that comply with the LICENSE and CLA

These marks MAY NOT be used for:
- Commercial products without a commercial license
- Misrepresentation of affiliation
- Derivative operating systems claiming to be “PantheonOS”
- Any use implying endorsement by B.H. or the PantheonOS Foundation

## Powered by PantheonOS™ Mark
Products integrating PantheonOS MUST apply for a trademark license to use:
“Powered by PantheonOS™”

This ensures:
- Quality standards are met
- Security and ethics invariants are preserved
- Attribution and authorship remain intact

For trademark licensing inquiries:
contact: pantheon-foundation@protonmail.com